    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1898-01-24T23:59:59-05:00"
                frus:doc-dateTime-min="1898-01-24T00:00:00-05:00" n="989"
                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d989">
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Mr. <persName type="from">Lee</persName> to Mr. <persName
                            type="to">Day</persName>.</hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Havana</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1898-01-24">
                            <hi rend="italic">January 24, 1898</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>Advise visit be postponed six or seven days, to give last excitement more time to
                    disappear. Will see authorities and let you know result. Governor-General away
                    for two weeks. I should know day and hour visit.</p>
            </div>
        </body>
